                <p>The female name Ἀθανώ is attested on at least seven occasions, primarily in the eastern half of the
                    Mediterranean according to
                    <ref target="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?name=Ἀθανώ">LGPN</ref>
                </p>
